title: Staples: Brother Label Maker ONLY $9.99 (Regularly $39.99)
text:
Looking to get organized? Head on over to Staples.com where they are offering up this highly rated Brother P-Touch PT-D210 Label Maker for only $9.99 (regularly $39.99).
This label maker is perfect for crafts, school supplies, getting your home office organized and more! This seems like a great deal as Amazon has this same model priced at $18.98 with fantastic reviews!
